         (m * (m - 1)) DIV 2 <= (m ** 2) DIV 2  by DIV_LE_MONOTONE
      so n ** ((m * (m - 1)) DIV 2) <= n ** ((m ** 2) DIV 2)   by EXP_BASE_LE_MONO, 1 < n
